metadata.name: PLC Financial Solutions Limited
metadata.description: PLC Financial Solutions Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the money lending activities in Australasia. It also provides short term lending solutions to small to medium sized enterprises. The company was formerly known as Global Gold Holdings Limited and changed its name to PLC Financial Solutions Limited in December 2017. PLC Financial Solutions Limited was incorporated in 2007 and is based in South Melbourne, Australia.
